{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"685","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"公司治理排名前5％ 25家上市櫃六連霸","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>04:10 2020/05/01 </span><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>工商時報 呂淑美、林燦澤</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%B2%BB%E7%90%86%E8%A9%95%E9%91%91%E9%87%8D%E9%BB%9E.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 572px;' />&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>第六屆上市公司公司治理評鑑重點</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<hr />\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>證交所及櫃買中心<span lang='EN-US'>30</span>日公布第六屆（<span lang='EN-US'>2019</span>年）公司治理評鑑排名，在第一級距、排序前<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>％的上市櫃公司中，台灣之光台積電等<span lang='EN-US'>25</span>家六連霸，六年來年年進榜前<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>％；另有<span lang='EN-US'>18</span>家為第六屆的新生力軍，其中，聚陽、永豐金、貿聯<span lang='EN-US'>-KY</span>、合庫金、醫揚及朋億等公司，為六屆來首度進榜前<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>％。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>上市櫃公司治理評鑑已完成六屆<span lang='EN-US'>901</span>家上市公司及<span lang='EN-US'>699</span>家上櫃公司，共<span lang='EN-US'>1,600</span>家列入評鑑。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>交易所統計，六屆年年蟬連前<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>％的上市公司，計有統一、東元、裕隆、中華、聯電、台積電、玉山金、統一超、台灣大、創意、遠傳、信義等<span lang='EN-US'>12</span>家公司，成為公司治理評鑑的標竿。此外，聚陽、永豐金、貿聯<span lang='EN-US'>-KY</span>及合庫金<span lang='EN-US'>4</span>家則為公司治理評鑑上路六屆以來，首度進榜前<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>％，與中鋼、南亞科、中華電、彰銀、富邦金、開發金、兆豐金、致伸及台汽電等<span lang='EN-US'>13</span>家為第六屆（與第五屆比）新進榜，光是金融股就有<span lang='EN-US'>6</span>家占了近半。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>櫃買市場方面，第六屆排名前<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>％共有<span lang='EN-US'>35</span>家上櫃公司，其中連續六屆都排名前<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>％的有穩懋、太醫、台微體、新鼎、立凱<span lang='EN-US'>-KY</span>、世界、中光電、中美晶、龍巖、寶雅、元大期、頎邦、崑鼎投控等<span lang='EN-US'>13</span>家上櫃公司，而新進榜名單則有醫揚、朋億、千附、光隆、明安等<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>家上櫃公司。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>另排名前<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>％上櫃企業還有安心、聯亞、艾訊、璟德、欣銓、精材、崇越電、兆利、東洋、智擎、杏一、湯石照明、聖暉、萬潤、環球晶、朋程、大江等，公司治理能力亮眼。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>證交所副總羅贊興指出，第六屆公司治理評鑑依得分情形，區分為前<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>％、<span lang='EN-US'>6</span>～<span lang='EN-US'>20</span>％、<span lang='EN-US'>21</span>～<span lang='EN-US'>35</span>％、<span lang='EN-US'>36</span>～<span lang='EN-US'>50</span>％、<span lang='EN-US'>51</span>～<span lang='EN-US'>65</span>％、<span lang='EN-US'>66</span>～<span lang='EN-US'>80</span>％，及<span lang='EN-US'>81</span>～<span lang='EN-US'>100</span>％等七個級距，分別依上市、上櫃受評公司公布評鑑結果。未來將持續強化公司治理評鑑效度，促進企業重視公司治理，落實企業社會責任，加速與國際接軌，增進資本市場發展。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>資料來源<span lang='EN-US'>: https://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20200501000200-260202?chdtv</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-05-01","clk_count":"165"}},"__N_SSG":true}